name: .DOV File Extension
summary: Learn about .DOV files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Temporary file created by a various programs; often deleted automatically when original file is saved or program is closed.

content: Temporary or "Temp" files most often use the .TMP extension. The ".dov" file extension may need to be changed back to the original extension in order to open correctly.
